column2: text:Give this card to the toy car. On your next turn, go forward to any free space and buy it. If all are owned, by one space from any player.
text:Advance to a brown or yellow space. If one is available get it for free, otherwise pay rent to the owner.
text:Advance to a light blue or red space. If one is available get it for free, otherwise pay rent to the owner.
text:Advance to a pink or dark blue space. If one is available get it for free, otherwise pay rent to the owner.
text:Advance to an orange or green space. If one is available get it for free, otherwise pay rent to the owner.
text:Advance to an orange space. If one is available get it for free, otherwise pay rent to the owner.
text:Advance to a red space. If one is available get it for free, Otherwise pay rent to the owner.
text:Advance to a light blue space. If one is available get it for free, otherwise pay rent to the owner.
Advance to the Skatepark. If no one owns it, get it for free, otherwise pay rent to the owner.
Advance to Boardwalk. If no one owns it, get it for free, otherwise pay rent to the owner.
